!!BC constants
!!     Cvtop*u00(my)+Cdyvtop*u00(my)=BC_top
!!     Cvbot*u00(1)+Cdyvbot*u00(1)=BC_bot
!!     
!!     TOP
!!    -----------
!!Dirichlet
